item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】WAV - Celine Dion - The Early Singles [44.1kHz 16bit]
item.description:
FORMAT: WAV 1411 kbps / 44.1 kHz / 16 bit
RELEASE: Celine Dion – The (Early) Singles (1999, CD) - Discogs

This compilation is the only CD were the song "L'amour Viendra" was released, apart from the previous vinyls. As oposite of the other pre 1990 french songs that Sony bought, that track wasn't released anymore on any compilations (like the On Ne Change Pas album).
Another song exclusive from this album, is the instrumental version of Ne Partez Pas Sans Moi, that was only released on vinyl previously.​

TRACKLIST:​
01 Ce N'était Qu'un Rêve
02 L'amour Viendra
03 D'amour Ou D'amitié
